n four pillars portfolio optimization operational excellence gotomarket effectiveness and process sustainability in the first quarter sunopta reported a loss of  million or  cents a share compared with a loss in the yearearlier period of  million or  cents a share the company also reported revenues of  million in the quarter a  percent decrease from  million a year earliercolo said the equipment sale fits into the company’s new strategy and will allow for the redeployment of capital for investment in more profitable parts of sunopta’s businessthe flexible resealable pouch business and aseptic beverage unit have appeared to be headed in different directions for quite some time consider the company’s fourthquarter results in while the new aseptic beverage operation in upper macungie was just ramping up and starting to win the company new business sunopta had to eat  million in costs because of downtime and spoilage resulting from an equipment failure during the quarter in the pouch side of the local plant caption elon musks longheld dream to revolutionize american driving seems almost within reach july   elon musks longheld dream to revolutionize american driving seems almost within reach july   caption elon musks longheld dream to revolutionize american driving seems almost within reach july   elon musks longheld dream to revolutionize american driving seems almost within reach july   caption jim donovan reports tsa uses social media to engage with travelers jim donovan reports tsa uses social media to engage with travelers caption sustainable energy fund president john costlow talks about the energypath  conference thursday at desales university in center valley sustainable energy fund president john costlow talks about the energypath  conference thursday at desales university in center valley caption in closing arguments alixandra smith told the jury that shkreli told investors he was managing  million when there were only a few hundred dollars in his firm’s broker